UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 562
1 A RESOLUTION confirming the appointment of Michael McGhee to the Board of
2 Directors of the Kentucky Employers' Mutual Insurance Authority.
3 WHEREAS, on March 13, 2026, in accordance with KRS 342.807 and by virtue of
4 Executive Order 2026-074, Governor Andy Beshear appointed Michael McGhee to the
5 Board of Directors of the Kentucky Employers' Mutual Insurance Authority for a term
6 expiring March 12, 2030; and
7 WHEREAS, the appointment is subject to Senate confirmation; and
8 WHEREAS, Michael McGhee has been determined to meet the requirements of
9 KRS 342.807;
10 NOW, THEREFORE,
11 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
12 Kentucky:
13 Section 1. The Senate hereby confirms the appointment of Michael McGhee to
14 the Board of Directors of the Kentucky Employers' Mutual Insurance Authority.
15 Section 2. The Clerk of the Senate shall forward a copy of this Resolution and
16 notification of its adoption to Michael McGhee of Elkton, Todd County, Kentucky and to
17 Governor Andy Beshear, 703 Capital Avenue, Room 133, Frankfort, Kentucky 40601.
